<title>mrsl mn rwḥk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mrsl mn rwḥk wbqwtk wmsẖ kẖạyf mn ạy sẖỷ

[V2]
 kl ạlly yhmny ạkẖdmk wạnt ḥạmyny ṭwl ạlṭryq

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - mạ ạnạ ʿmry fy ạydk mḍmwn wạlṣʿb mʿạk ạnt yhwn

[V4]
 wạlkẖṭr dh mhmạ ykwn ạnạ mʿạyạ qwẗ rwḥk

[V5]
 2- mṭmn jdạaⁿ wạnạ jnbk lạnk ạnt fy mrkby

[V6]
 wạtẖq dạymạaⁿ fyk wfy ḥbk dh ạnt fy ʿynk btṣwny

[V7]
 3- mrsl bslạmk rby wfrḥ wbtʿzyạt mnk wnwr

[V8]
 byk hạfḍl sạyr lạ ạnṭrḥ sẖạmkẖ wʿạly zy ạlnswr</lyrics>
